cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.NE 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing tasks such as argument reasoning comprehension. It could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it uses a neural network architecture for the task. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) as the model is trained on large machine translation datasets and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it uses LSTMs for the task.
